There is also at least one [ring-rider](https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_SG/story/jinx-color-story/), though it's probably wrapped 'round a tree after Jinx took it for a joy ride.  (Ring-rider concept [here](https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/region/piltover/), under 'Hextech' I believe.)

{{sticker:zombie-nunu-tears}} 

(But when I think Piltover/Zaun, I definitely think of the Rising Howl and other Hexdraulic-Conveyors, described in [Blitzcrank's story](https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/story/blitzcrank-color-story/), the [City of Iron and Glass](https://universe.leagueoflegends.com/en_US/story/zaun-cityironglass/) story (though they might want to sterilize that glass roof), and shown in [Camille's comic](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/camille-comic) .)
